<body>
    <h1>OpenFin &amp; W1C &#39;Intent&#39; Workshop Minutes</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><u>Workshop:</u> W1 &amp; W1C Customer Portal to assess and deve=
lop the solution for implementing the Multiverse NPM Library</p>
<p><u>Attendees:bStuart Johnson &lt;stuart.johnson@<a href=3D"http://westpa=
c.com.au" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; =
Gary Baldock &lt;gary.baldock@<a href=3D"http://westpac.com.au" class=3D"ex=
ternal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; Jeremy Roberts &lt;je=
remyroberts@<a href=3D"http://westpac.com.au" class=3D"external-link" rel=
=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; Bobby Joseph &lt;bobby.joseph@<a href=
=3D"http://westpac.com.au" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac=
.com.au</a>&gt;; Rachita Sharma &lt;rachita.sharma@<a href=3D"http://westpa=
c.com.au" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; =
Oliver Wu &lt;oliver.wu@<a href=3D"http://westpac.com.au" class=3D"external=
-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; Ave Cahyadi &lt;ave.cahyadi=
@<a href=3D"http://westpac.com.au" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow"=
>westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; Nathaniel Chen &lt;nathaniel.chen@<a href=3D"http:=
//westpac.com.au" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</=
a>&gt;; Thomas Van Deun &lt;thomas.vandeun@<a href=3D"http://westpac.com.au=
" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;; Zoe Shir=
ley &lt;zoe.shirley@<a href=3D"http://westpac.com.au" class=3D"external-lin=
k" rel=3D"nofollow">westpac.com.au</a>&gt;</u></p>
<p><u>Agenda:</u> For W1C to provide requirements for Openfin regarding the=
 Customer Portal (only at this stage):</p>
<ul>
<li>What =E2=80=98intents=E2=80=99 to define, and how many,</li>
<li>How do we break down the current W1C MFEs,</li>
<li>What are =E2=80=98contexts=E2=80=99</li>
</ul>
<p><u>Inputs:</u> All current W1C Customer Portal screens across all custom=
er journeys</p>
<p><u>Minutes &amp; Actions:</u></p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>SSO and session management was parked for this workshop - BJ noted ISG =
consideration of not having session management for February release</li>
<li>Agreed that Feb25 ERM is the basic enablement of Galaxy in OpenFin. TVD=
 suggested that intents may not be necessary to meet this milestone. SJ req=
uested that the ViewAccountActivity intent is included in Feb to test the c=
oncept.</li>
<li>AN advised that consolidated Account List is targeted for Aug25 ERM. No=
ted that these intents can be deprioritised for Feb.</li>
<li>AN advised that consolidated Payment List is out-of-scope for MVP (targ=
et MMP). SJ suggested this should be brought forward to MVP if possible.</l=
i>
<li>Agreed that splitting of MFEs will not be in-scope for Feb25 ERM</li>
<li>SJ advised that Tech assumption is that Staff Portal is in-scope for Op=
enFin enablement in Feb25 ERM. AN noted that the strategic decision to util=
ise OpenFin for the W1C Staff Portal is TBC with Lipsa (W1C) and Sue (W1).<=
/li>
<li>Dependency on W1 to deliver Navigator for Feb25 ERM</li>
<li>Action: AN to schedule similar workshop for Staff Portal next week</li>
</ul>
<p><u>Output:</u> W1C Customer Portal List of 'Intents' and Applications</p=
>
<p></p>
